comments: Wiggins (GSW) legally contests Garland's (CLE) play at the basket.
Mitchell (CLE) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Thompson's (GSW) arm before Thompson makes his intended pass.
Curry (GSW) brings his off-arm toward Garland (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as Curry (GSW) releases away without applying any force.
Green (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Curry (GSW) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's (CLE) arm after the release.

Looney (GSW) and Allen (CLE) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound. As they disengage, Green (GSW) steps in front of Allen to box out and marginal lower body contact occurs.
Curry (GSW) is moving alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs as they briefly come together during the drive.
Mitchell (CLE) gathers on his right foot and then jump stops, which allows him to choose either foot as his pivot. He chooses his right foot as his pivot and maintains it.
Initially, Green (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Allen (CLE). Allen regains possession and Green reaches for the ball again and makes contact with Allen's face, which affects his SQBR.
Thompson (GSW) does not give Okoro (CLE) the time or distance to avoid the contact and turns his shoulder to deliver contact, which dislodges Okoro during the pick.
Green (GSW) and Love (CLE) mutually engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Mobley (CLE) commits a take foul on Wiggins (GSW).
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Okoro (CLE) moves into and delivers body contact to Curry (GSW), which affects Curry's SQBR during the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Green (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Green (GSW) moves into Mitchell's (CLE) path and initiates leg to leg contact that affects his SQBR and causes him to trip.
Curry (GSW) legally contests Garland's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Mobley (CLE) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
